-- Japan finance minister: to make comment after G7 phone meeting
-- 
-- Sun Aug 7, 2011 4:45pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/07/us-japan-economy-g-idUSTRE7762OT20110807

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Japanese Finance Minister Yoshihiko Noda said on Monday that he would make comment after a telephone meeting between the finance leaders of the Group of Seven major industrialised nations. 

 (Reporting by  Tetsushi Kajimoto ; Editing by  Joseph Radford )